HEADWORD: Cartbote
<hw>Cart"bote`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[<ets>Cart</ets> +
<ets>bote</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Old Eng. Law.)</fld> <def>Wood to which a
